<h1>Meet Our Team</h1>

<p class="introduction">Bigger Bird has the design sense, technical capabilities and most importantly, the experience necessary to create a successful web site that meets your specific needs. We understand and respect deadlines, and we reserve time every month just for you. We have both experience <strong>and</strong> enthusiasm, so we do not train on your dime. Our dependable and knowledgeable support team is always ready to answer any questions you may have.</p>

