    <p>Charles has spent nearly half of his life immersing himself in the latest web technologies. Since joining our team in 2007, he has already increased our standard of quality by improving our compliance with emerging web standards.</p>
    
    <p>When he's not developing web sites, he enjoys such artistic pursuits as photography and typography. Also topping his list are travel and exploring the great outdoors.</p>
    
